  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为零售收银系统（Retail_PointOfSale）设计一个状态流转图。核心场景是：收银员从初始状态开始，通过扫描操作进入签到状态，最终完成服务。另外还要处理一种异常情况——如果还没签到就扫了结束码，要报错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Error",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是Retail_PointOfSale，然后分出两条路：正常路径是Absent→CheckedIn→Attended，异常路径是Absent直接到Error。请问CheckedIn之后如果又扫了Start码，是停留在CheckedIn还是转到其他状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CheckedIn状态下如果扫Start码，相当于重新签到，还是留在CheckedIn。但如果是扫End码，就进入Attended服务中状态。另外Attended状态下扫任何码都保持不动，只是要记录是来自Retail_CouponSystem的操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Start",
        "End",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Retail_PointOfSale初始化到Absent，Absent通过\"Start\"扫描到CheckedIn，CheckedIn通过\"End\"扫描到Attended。同时补充CheckedIn的自循环，以及Attended的自循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Start",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要补充异常处理：Absent状态下如果误扫了End码，而且这个动作来自Retail_OrderManagement，就要进入Error状态。Error状态必须能重置回Absent，比如点击\"清除错误\"按钮。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "Error",
        "End",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Сброс / Очистка ошибки"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Error状态的触发条件是\"扫描End码（Retail_OrderManagement）\"，对吗？另外我在Error右边加个注释，说明这是Retail_PointOfSale上的无效操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "End",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错。还有个小细节：CheckedIn的自循环触发条件是扫描Start码且来自Retail_Inventory系统，这个和主流程的Start码要区分开来源。Attended的自循环则是Start或End都可以，但只关联Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Start",
        "End",
